{"tid":1172724,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[小小遊記］柬埔寨，生活既意義","createTime":"2019-05-26T15:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T09:57:04.000Z","uid":136793,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"08777ed6185e66a288256d3f6ad0f585b41d2bef","tid":1172724,"uid":136793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:30:30.000Z","msg":"第一次打遊記，雖然唔會話好詳盡，只係少少咁講下講下，但有好大感想想記錄下，又唔知可以同邊個講下好，所以就打上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單講下行程先，其實去6日5夜，行程都離唔開吳哥窟、酒吧街同埋酒店。除左睇吳哥窟外，最想就係好好放鬆下自己。到最後真係達到左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳哥窟入面啲野就唔多介紹，我都只係上網睇左一睇資料，去到國家博物館睇下睇，就直接去啦。俾少少相大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LPUCbOm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLPUCbOm.png&h=3e401268&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳哥城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQfBsmH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQfBsmH.png&h=bb67f6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳哥的微笑<br />\n<br />\n第一次去柬埔寨，去之前仲以為會好混亂，係一個未發展既城市，以為機場會收賄，以為去到會唔安全，以為呢個地方好落後，以為啲人都淨係識講佢地語言好難溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到先發現柬埔寨已經發展左好多，雖然佢地為主既係旅遊業（我覺得），但總算係幫助到佢地發展。連機場都貼左唔使額外收費既紙條，仲有人監督<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做足哂準備要俾人打回頭幾次同埋點樣扮唔明tips係咩，到最後都無用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但點解我會話佢地主要發展旅遊業？當然最重要係吳哥窟既影響。到處都係Tuktuk，佢地會係咁捕住你，無論係條街定係係吳哥窟，都會走去你身邊：「TukTuk? 漂亮喔，我愛你，要坐我的Tuktuk嗎？回酒店嗎？TukTuk&hellip;TukTuk&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ev9Nob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ev9Nob.png&h=1dbd707f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地個Tuktuk司機好好食，一開頭收左我地USD$3，我同朋友都以為佢有開大我地價（話哂上網睇過過啲Tuktuk司機好鍾意開大一兩倍價），點知之後有啲司機車我地同樣距離夠膽開USD$10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地即刻調頭走，佢就死死地氣追上黎&ldquo;$5 Okay okay&rdquo;，當然，一知佢開大個價既都唔想再上佢架車，因為係暹粒既Tuktuk其實唔難搵，岩岩都講過，佢地會圍住你，所以，要搵一個唔會開大價既司機都唔係好難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到吳哥窟入面，好多小朋友同婦女係到賣野，小朋友我估6歲到10幾歲都有，普通話，英文都講得好好，仲有啲日文韓文都識。佢地會用好可憐既眼神望住你，然後由頭跟你跟到尾。如果係婦女，佢地會話: Lady, you need something? Buy something? 另外，仲有啲青年，畫畫叻啲既就係吳哥窟入面邊畫邊賣。基本上星期一至五都會有，有時都會不禁令我同朋友諗：咁細個就要幫屋企出黎幫補家計，學識幾種言語，都幾可憐。好似全家大細，不論大細男女，都要出黎幫手賺錢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7vt2Yg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7vt2Yg.png&h=30de47db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫畫既青年，但佢其實畫緊另一個廟既畫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUj27pX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUj27pX.png&h=ad637cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲小朋友係吳哥窟入面等遊客到，講解下果個廟既事，再話幫你影番一兩張相，然後就&ldquo;Tips, tips!&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M1NTuDi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1NTuDi.png&h=490062c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（原諒有啲低清，係張相入面再cap出黎）仲有啲小朋友就咁企係啲暗啲、入啲既位，叫你俾錢俾糖。"},{"pid":"26ad2e7a40684993e7cf2d2924cc287afac24fb2","tid":1172724,"uid":28195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"會唔會去S21參觀？"},{"pid":"973fbc5a26c85f865813a674e228e44a3ef3af37","tid":1172724,"uid":96,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:50:30.000Z","msg":"之前去頭兩日就咁叫tuktuk佢地開到勁貴<br />\n跟住先識down grab 平一半有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就咁叫tuktuk去啲好近嘅地方佢地都開5蚊 後尾用grab係酒吧街去機場先5蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f422f0778eb674ff4ff8a44ca3fa27e7c8beb47d","tid":1172724,"uid":237112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"分享好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3005afc1adb03a65c8a296002fa18628392920","tid":1172724,"uid":136793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26ad2e7a40684993e7cf2d2924cc287afac24fb2","tid":1172724,"uid":28195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:47:45.000Z","msg":"會唔會去S21參觀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:10:16.000Z","msg":"我已經番左黎啦，原本都有睇過下，但係我同朋友都好細膽果啲，少少恐怖都會瞓唔著發幾日惡夢，所以都唔太敢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9485e3fe9bba2eb48f123d83bbf2de321a18ac21","tid":1172724,"uid":136793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"973fbc5a26c85f865813a674e228e44a3ef3af37","tid":1172724,"uid":96,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:50:30.000Z","msg":"之前去頭兩日就咁叫tuktuk佢地開到勁貴<br />\n跟住先識down grab 平一半有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就咁叫tuktuk去啲好近嘅地方佢地都開5蚊 後尾用grab係酒吧街去機場先5蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:11:28.000Z","msg":"係！我都有down定grab，但因為我地已經摸哂佢地既底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以到最後一次grab都無用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c268f903ae3cfe5fb36963eadd749c0e6ef53c3c","tid":1172724,"uid":34007,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T00:12:50.000Z","msg":"食happy pizza<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd5a8f1b91274162e9260398c144c70a1a7603b","tid":1172724,"uid":57844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"好多年前去過, 跟團<br />\n一落旅遊巴, D細路用即影即有幫你影相, 到上番巴時就埋黎問你買<br />\n$1 美金一張, 果時都無人買."},{"pid":"b55665ac7db0bfe0490d7fc52f567fb5e8ef5b77","tid":1172724,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"f189d236ca358d4950ba7993af6973be8a4826ce","tid":1172724,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"食蟲<br />\n一定要"},{"pid":"735cd8338ee8a9b3c14464d30ad5ab36a783a971","tid":1172724,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"一個絲自己去?"},{"pid":"e0139e580fe1006d1d97d244566a5f65dbc449a9","tid":1172724,"uid":155027,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"絲打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到你呢篇先醒起自己個篇柬蒲寨爛左尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d6d17ed63fe47b329fd0267b0aece845bc7ef5","tid":1172724,"uid":39689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:37:44.000Z","msg":"加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3991d577139ab6854385a6cf9a2d32236a5b1bdb","tid":1172724,"uid":170365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:44:42.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4f3cae5de4e67cb2704ee5aea6faf396a5fe7b05","tid":1172724,"uid":48958,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"去到先發現柬埔寨已經發展左好多，雖然佢地為主既係旅遊業（我覺得），但總算係幫助到佢地發展。<br />\n<br />\n其實暹粒代唔代表到成個柬埔寨呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6035fa48ca5bb291a048240868aeebce58cff62e","tid":1172724,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"留名 準備去"},{"pid":"05c39556619ac31a55877aeb6838668c18b3f0b2","tid":1172724,"uid":25356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"我去呢啲國家買野好小講價講到盡，覺得唔太貴就算。<br />\n心底希望佢地因爲我賺多左既錢佢地會用係下一代身上"},{"pid":"6291f525b30543254afa059d5e68c4f0a6665878","tid":1172724,"uid":7332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"05c39556619ac31a55877aeb6838668c18b3f0b2","tid":1172724,"uid":25356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":